      "created_at": "2022-01-08T12:19:26.141Z",
      "cooked": "<p>There is at least one other app that can control this ergometer, but I can\u2019t find any clear statement on FTMS compatibility (FTMS is the protocol used for Smart trainers).<br>\nMyHomeFIT app (Android only) is free to use with adds or a add-free version for a one time payment of 10\u20ac.<br>\nIt looks like it should be controllable in Power mode but I can\u2019t make out what protocol is needed.<br>\nHere\u2019s a YouTube link explaining it all from 22:30 mark on. It\u2019s in German so I only understand partly what he\u2019s saying\u2026 Maybe someone with good knowledge of German can give extra help?</p><div class=\"youtube-onebox lazy-video-container\" data-video-id=\"mK5zU13VcHI\" data-video-title=\"Christopeit ET6 Pro Ergometer Test / ERGOMETER &amp; HEIMTRAINER\" data-video-start-time=\"1355\" data-provider-name=\"youtube\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mK5zU13VcHI&amp;t=1355\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"video-thumbnail\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">\n    <img class=\"youtube-thumbnail\" src=\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/mK5zU13VcHI/maxresdefault.jpg\" title=\"Christopeit ET6 Pro Ergometer Test / ERGOMETER &amp; HEIMTRAINER\" width=\"690\" height=\"388\">\n  </a>\n</div>\n",
